Package: extr
Title: Extinction Risk Estimation
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Hiroshi", "Hakoyama", , "hiroshi.hakoyama@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7464-0754"))
Description: Estimates extinction probabilities from time series of
    population sizes based on a Wiener-drift process model. Implements the
    w-z method (Hakoyama, 2025) to improve the accuracy of confidence
    intervals over conventional approaches.
